title: Danny & Luke MacFarlane (Bros)
itunes:title: Danny & Luke MacFarlane (Bros)
description:
Danny chats with the charming Luke MacFarlane, star of the new movie BROS (out September 30)! They discuss the film, Exit to Eden, Hallmark Christmas movies, plus Danny asks all his pressing questions about Luke's other iconic role, Scotty in Brothers & Sisters!
